{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tomehr wiꞥſch atminneja to wezzu Laiku/ Mohſu un wiꞥſa Laudis. Kur irr tas/ kaſ tehs no Juhras irr iſweddis ar teem Ganneem ſawa ganna.ma Pulka? Kur irr/ kaſ ſawu Swehtu Garru wiꞥſno Widdi dewe?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kaſ Mohſu pee labbas Rohkas wedde/ zaur to Elkonu ſawas Gohdibas/ kaſ to Uhdeni wiꞥſu Preeſcha dalliſa/ un darrija ſew weenu muhſchign Wahrdn.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kaſ tohs waddija zaur teem Besdibbineem/ ka weenu Sirgu Tukfueți/un tee ne kluppe.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Itt ka Lohps/ kaſ no-eet Geleijâ/ ta irr ta KUNGA Gars teem Duffeschannu dewis. Ta eſti tu tawus Laudis waddijs/ ka tu ſew weenu apgoḣdinatu Wahrdn darritu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Raugi no Debbeṣ/ un noſkattajs no tawas fwehtas un gohdigas Weetas. Kur irr ta-wa karſta Mihleſtiba un tawu Warra? tawa leela Sirds Eſchehloſhana un tawas Schehlaſtibaṣ? tahs turrahs zeeti prett manni.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu tomehr eſti muhſu Tehws/ jo Ahbraams ne ſinna wiꞥſch tam darrihs/ kaſ us wiꞥſmuhs/ un Iſraëls ne paſihſt muhs. Tu ak KUNGS! eſti muhſu Tehws/ muhſu Peſtitajs/ no wezzeem Laifeem irr tas taws Wahrdṣ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "KUNGS/ kapehz leeẓ tumuns no taweem Zeſkeem maſditees? Kapehz leeẓ tu muhſu Sirdi apzeeinatees/ ka mehs te-wis ne bihſtamees? atgreeſee-tawu Kalpu deht/ to Zilschu ta-was Eemantofchunas labbad.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tee gann drihs turr ta-wus fwehtus Laudis par Jhpa-fchunu/ muhſu Prettineeki irrtawu fwehtu Weetu ſaininnu-fchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Mehs eſſam tappufchi itt ka tee/ pahr kurreein tu muhſchi-gi ne eſti waldijs/ un kaſ pehz tawu Wahrdn ne irr noſaukti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ak! Kaut tu tahṣ Debbe-fiſ taplohtiṭu/ ka tu nonahktu/ ka tee Kalni iſkustu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Itt ka Kauteschanas Ug-guns deg/ un ka Ugguns to Uh-deni darra uſwehrdam. Ka taws Wahrdṣ taptu paſihſtans dar-rihts taween Prettineekeim/ ka tee Pagani tawa Preeſcha drebbetu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Rad tu bihjajamas Leetas darriji/ ko mehs ne buhtum gai-diſchi/ tu nolaidees/ tawa Preeſ-châ iſkuſe tee Kalui.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ir muhſcham ne irr dſir-dehtṣ/ nedṣ ar Autim faman-nihtṣ/ nedṣ rahda Azz irr redſej-fi/ bes tewis ween ak Dewṣ! ko kaſ us wiꞥſ\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu faſtappi tohs Preezi-gus/ un kaſ to Taifnibu darrija/ kaſ tewis perminneja us taween Zeſkeem. (Redſi/ tu bijt apſkat-teṣ/\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
